## Limitations

The analysis is based on data and reports available up to October 2023. The dynamic nature of global oil markets means that new developments could alter the current understanding of price trends. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may introduce biases inherent in the original reporting. Further research and real-time data analysis would be necessary for a more comprehensive understanding.